{"tid":941551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父母籌不到10萬聘金供他結婚　男怒喝農藥自殺","createTime":"2018-12-15T01:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T08:05:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d6328b7faa3a161c4ff8844f2b996eb76515dcd3","tid":941551,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"中國江蘇南京一名20歲的王姓男子，雖然想要結婚，但付不出女方家人要求的10萬元人民幣（約44.64萬元台幣）聘金，他向父母開口要錢，偏偏家裡沒錢，於是想不開飲農藥自殺。 警方指，王男與女友已論及婚嫁，但在餐廳打工的王男，沒有能力籌到聘金，而他父母都是打工的，家裡也沒這麼多錢&hellip;&hellip;後來（王男）跟父親打電話要錢不成，就丟下一句：『不給錢我就喝農藥！』」員警獲報後，趕到王男打工的餐廳，發現他「說到做到」，已經口吐白沫、昏迷在地，送醫後醫生開出病危通知，但後來被救回，已經脫離危險期。王父無奈地說，大家都為聘金的事苦惱，但家裡就是窮，沒想到他會為此做傻事。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAvnbgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAvnbgO.png&h=3c97b6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrK3E99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrK3E99.png&h=c1d91c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50x8RgP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50x8RgP.png&h=60056fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUHQkaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUHQkaa.png&h=df2ac9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181215/1484123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181215%2F1484123&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=76c52b88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181215%2F1484123&h=d6282f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181215/1484123</a>"},{"pid":"135598cdbf57cf3acb0a6efed636fbfa4bf68358","tid":941551,"uid":179467,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:44:35.000Z